---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Integration Dashboard">
  <div class="dashboard-hero">
    <p class="tagline">Lightning-fast, memory-safe API integration with local semantic vector search, autopilot crawlers, and RAG optimization.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="section-title">Core Systems Overview</h2>
  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">🤖</div>
      <h3>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</h3>
      <p>Exposes search and facets tools directly to LLM agents using async JSON-RPC over standard input/output channels.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Agentic Query Autopilot</h3>
      <p>Recursively splits search scopes based on year counts to crawl deep datasets past the API limit boundaries.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">🔍</div>
      <h3>Local Semantic Search</h3>
      <p>Offline sentence embeddings generation and cosine similarity sorting computed on-device using the `candle` ML crate.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">🐍</div>
      <h3>Python FFI Bindings</h3>
      <p>FFI mapping using `pyo3` and `maturin` to import native compiled client performance straight into Jupyter Notebooks.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .dashboard-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05));
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
